#### Short Message Service (SMS)
Also known as text messaging.

#### E-Mail
Email is "electronic mail". There are several components to a working email system:

* email sending and receiving via mailer daemons over the SMTP protocol
* email access and transfer via email transfer daemons over the POP or IMAP protocols
* email clients or readers for viewing and management of individual email mailboxes

'''Example Email Mailer Daemons'''
* Sendmail
* Postfix

'''Email Transfer Daemons'''
* [[Courier]]
* Dovecot

'''Email Clients'''
* Outlook Express
* Apple Mac Mail.app
* Thunderbird
* Entourage

